subject: Order Approving the Supplementary Letters Patent Provision Amending Article 9 of the Letters Patent Issued to the Toronto Port Authority
precis: Order Amending the Toronto Port Authority Letters Patent in order to increase the limit on the power of the Toronto Port Authority to borrow money on its credit for port purposes from $52.1 million to $185 million.
